00:04:08.049 --> 00:04:11.909
In the end, only Jackson knew his true motivation
for ultimately choosing to bleach his skin,

00:04:11.909 --> 00:04:16.840
whether as a treatment for his vitiligo to
even out his skin color as reported, or as

00:04:16.840 --> 00:04:21.980
the conspiracy theorists claim, to further
change his appearance to more of a Caucasian

00:04:21.980 --> 00:04:26.080
look, though one would think the latter would
be an odd move for the co-author of the line

00:04:26.080 --> 00:04:36.160
(with Bill Bottrell), “It don’t matter
if you’re black 

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:40.580
or white.”

